%[text] **W: expected total time in the system, waiting plus service time** 
%[text] $W=\\frac{1}{\\left(\\mu \\;-\\frac{\\;\\lambda \\;}{2}\\right)\\left(1+\\frac{\\;\\lambda \\;}{\\mu {\\;}\_2 }\\right)}=\\frac{1}{\\left(30\\;-\\frac{\\;40\\;}{2}\\right)\\left(1+\\frac{\\;40\\;}{60}\\right)}=\\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{\\;20\\;}{2}\\right)\\left(\\frac{\\;100\\;}{60}\\right)}=\\frac{1}{\\left(10\\right)\\left(\\frac{\\;5\\;}{3}\\right)}=\\frac{3}{50}=\\ldotp 06${"editStyle":"visual"} hours
%[text] (.06)(60) = 3.6 minutes
